            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Iulius Bellicus <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>alae Asturum II <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>municipi</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cla</abbr><ex>udiae</ex></expan> Celeiae <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berius</ex></expan> Iulius Frontonis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Civis <lb n="6"/>frater et heres fecit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sockel eines größeren Grabdenkmals (ev. Pfeilergrabmal?). Material: weißer Marmor aus Pohorje. Autopsie J. Visočnik. Metadaten ergänzt nach CIL 03-neu (in Vorbereitung; Bearbeiterin: J. Visočnik).</p>
            </div>
